						<summary>

						<p>Damaged and ends of lines lost. Seems to register a gift (details lost) by <hi rend="bold">Chiṅga-Daṇḍēśa (Siṅgaṇṇa Daṇḍanāyaka),</hi> minister of Hoysaḷa <hi rend="bold">Sōmēśvara,</hi> in the <hi rend="bold">32nd regnal year</hi> of the king. The details of the date viz., •••••, śu ••• śī, Sunday and Uttiraṭṭādi probably corresponds to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1247, October 13, Sunday,</hi> (Trayōdaśī) ·98; ·63. The month was Tulā.</p>						

						</summary>
